    "product_details_gLrgBJ": {
      "type": "product-details",
      "blocks": {
        "description_w7TU9P": {
          "type": "description",
          "settings": {
            "description_heading": "Introduction"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_PAyNwP": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Key Features",
            "content": "<ul><li><strong>18 Driver Balanced Armature + EST Architecture</strong></li><li><strong>Quad Electrostatic Driver</strong></li><li><strong>Gemstone Faceplate Design</strong></li><li><strong>7 Way Passive Crossover</strong></li><li><strong>4 Woofer | 2 Bass | 2 Mid-Bass | 2 Mid | 2 Mid-High | 2 High | 4 Electrostatic Super Tweeter</strong></li><li><strong>48\" Epsilon+ Monocrystalline IEM Cable 4.4mm Balanced</strong></li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_n38dzJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The Most Sophisticated Transducer Architecture",
            "content": "<p>Beneath Mokara’s sculptural elegance lies a marvel of acoustic engineering: an 18-driver hybrid architecture combining balanced armature and electrostatic technologies. At its core is a meticulously arranged 7-way passive crossover, directing a symphony of specialized drivers—4 woofers, 2 bass, 2 mid-bass, 2 mid, 2 mid-high, and 2 high—each tuned for precise control across the entire frequency spectrum. Crowned by 4 electrostatic super tweeters, Mokara delivers an ultra-extended treble response with astonishing air and microdetail. This sophisticated configuration creates an effortlessly natural and immersive soundstage, where every layer, from thunderous lows to whisper-fine highs, is revealed in stunning fidelity.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_fPHfQE": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "“Sandwich” Hybrid Enclosure Design",
            "content": "<p>Mokara’s construction is a testament to the harmony of<br/>cutting-edge technology and artisanal craftsmanship, brought together in a<br/>sophisticated “sandwich” hybrid enclosure design. At its foundation is a<br/>precision-engineered 3D-printed acoustic chamber, enabling complex internal<br/>geometries that optimize airflow and resonance control for uncompromising sound<br/>performance. This is seamlessly integrated with a CNC-machined aluminum<br/>mid-case, selected not only for its modern aesthetic but also for its<br/>structural rigidity—particularly around the reinforced 2-pin connector stock,<br/>ensuring long-term durability and a secure cable interface. Capping this<br/>layered design is a handcrafted resin-based faceplate, each one individually<br/>poured and polished to reveal mesmerizing swirls and vibrant color gradients.<br/>This multi-material approach results in a shell that is both acoustically<br/>superior and visually captivating, reflecting the same precision and beauty<br/>found in Mokara’s sound signature.<strong> </strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_HffCBq": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Exclusive Gemstone Faceplate Design",
            "content": "<p>Experience the perfect fusion of artistry<br/>and sound with our <strong>Opal Infused Faceplate Design. </strong>Crafted with<br/>meticulous attention to detail, each faceplate is a masterpiece, showcasing<br/>genuine opal gemstones that shimmer with captivating hues of blues, greens, and<br/>fiery reds, creating a design as unique as your music taste. Beyond their<br/>stunning aesthetics, these IEMs deliver unparalleled audio clarity, enveloping<br/>you in every note, beat, and nuance. Whether you're a musician, audiophile, or<br/>style enthusiast, our opal-accented IEMs redefine luxury and performance,<br/>turning your listening experience into a visual and auditory marvel.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_XefaKL": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Accessories and Warranty",
            "content": "<ul><li>Null Audio Epsilon+ Monocrystalline IEM Cable</li><li>AAW Carrying Case</li><li>Cleaning Cloth</li><li>SpinFit Universal Ear Tips</li><li>Assorted Foam & Silicone Ear Tips</li><li>2 Year Limited Warranty</li></ul>"
          }
        },
