            "heading": "Epsilon+ Premium Upgrade Cable",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "seo_heading": "h3",
            "description": "<p>The Epsilon+ cable, featuring a cryogenically treated monocrystalline copper conductor and UPOCC cast, ensures unparalleled accuracy and vocal definition, removing any veil from the music. Null Audio has customized a new Y-splitter for the Mokara, adorned with a delicate geometry carved plate completes its unique appearance.</p>"
